      <guid>https://josuecorujo.github.io/slides/2022-10-nancy/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;simulations-for-the-augmented-multiplicative-coalescent&#34;&gt;Simulations for the (augmented) multiplicative coalescent&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;!-- [Wowchemy](https://wowchemy.com/) | [Documentation](https://wowchemy.com/docs/content/slides/) --&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
$$ B_t(s) = W_t(s) - \inf_{0 \leq u \leq s} W_t(u),$$&lt;p&gt; where $ W_t(s) = W(s) - \frac{1}{2}s^2 + t s $.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$X_i(t)$: $i$th largest excursion of $B_t(\cdot)$ above zero,&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$\big( \pmb{X}(t), t \ge 0  \big) $ is a realization of an eternal multiplicative coalescent.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;















&lt;figure  id=&#34;figure-w_ts--ws---fracs22--t-s-for-t--05&#34;&gt;
